UML:TaggedValue.value: Must generate test cases for document-based web services using SOA
Should support doc, docx, rtf and html document formats
Must generate protocol for testing, including rationale for each test and possible outcomes
Must support orphan analysis of system design models

Should support change impact analysis in minimum 2 levels depth
